05 Aug 2010 22:17






This is pretty good. It's not amazing or anything, but I really like the origin story you gave to the factory. Hell, once you're done with this, you might want to add your version of "The Factory" to the SCP-001 proposals.

My biggest problem with this is that it seems to tell too much about the foundation. It neatly spells out the Foundation's origin, as well as the origin of a few other rival organizations. Some people like the Foundation to be all mysterious and vague. And while I like getting answers, these answers arn't as… erm, "world shattering" as, say, Dr Clef's Proposal (I liked the reference to it, though). Hell, I'm surprised a dozen idiots haven't called you a moron for writing something like this.

I'm going to hold my vote for when you're done. But hey, don't let me stop you.





